WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:01.760
Barclays Online Banking

2
00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:05.960
How to log in to Online Banking
with Mobile PINsentry

3
00:00:06.520 --> 00:00:10.920
It’s easy to log in to your Barclays Online Banking
account using PINsentry.

4
00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:15.920
If you're registered for Online Banking,
you can use your membership number,

5
00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:19.760
card number, or sort code
and account number to log in.

6
00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:22.240
Start by entering your last name

7
00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:25.000
as well as your sort code and account number.

8
00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:27.600
If you're using your private computer,

9
00:00:27.880 --> 00:00:31.040
you can tick the box to remember
your login credentials.

10
00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:33.480
Then click ‘Continue’.

11
00:00:33.880 --> 00:00:37.080
Open the Barclays app
and select ‘PINsentry’.

12
00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:41.920
Once open, select ‘Identify’
and enter your passcode.

13
00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:46.560
Once you're logged into PINsentry
you will be given an access code.

14
00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:52.320
Enter this 8-digit access code on your
Barclay's Online Banking login screen.

15
00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:57.840
Then select ‘Log in to Online Banking’
at the bottom of the page.

16
00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:00.240
And that's it.

17
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:04.240
Logging in to
Barclays Online Banking made simple

18
00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:06.960
with the help of Mobile PINsentry.

